description: Retrieve details of an EnabledBaseline resource by specifying its identifier.

parameters.name: enabledBaselineIdentifier
parameters.description: Identifier of the EnabledBaseline resource to be retrieved, in ARN format.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The ARN of the EnabledBaseline resource.

nested_items.name: baselineIdentifier
nested_items.description: The specific Baseline enabled as part of the EnabledBaseline resource.

nested_items.name: baselineVersion
nested_items.description: The enabled version of the Baseline.

nested_items.name: parameters
nested_items.description: Shows the parameters that are applied when enabling this Baseline.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: A string denoting the parameter key.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: A low-level document object of any type (for example, a Java Object).

nested_items.name: parentIdentifier
nested_items.description: An ARN that represents the parent EnabledBaseline at the Organizational Unit (OU) level, from which the child EnabledBaseline inherits its configuration. The value is returned by GetEnabledBaseline.

nested_items.name: statusSummary
nested_items.description: The deployment summary of an EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline resource.

nested_items.name: lastOperationIdentifier
nested_items.description: The last operation identifier for the enabled resource.

nested_items.name: status
nested_items.description: The deployment status of the enabled resource.
SUCCEEDED: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration was deployed successfully.
UNDER_CHANGE: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration is changing.
FAILED: The EnabledControl or EnabledBaseline configuration failed to deploy.

nested_items.name: targetIdentifier
nested_items.description: The target on which to enable the Baseline.
